    <item>
      <title>中国贷款下降引发“资产负债表”衰退担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/china-s-rare-loan-drop-stokes-fears-of-balance-sheet-recession</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国近二十年来首次缩减银行贷款，引发人们担忧中国这一全球第二大经济体正像日本几十年前那样陷入“资产负债表衰退”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/china-s-rare-loan-drop-stokes-fears-of-balance-sheet-recession</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 03:42:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球最大钢铁生产商警告“严重”危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/china-steel-industry-in-crisis-as-baowu-warns-of-severe-winter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这家全球最大钢铁生产商警告称，中国钢铁行业正面临比 2008 年和 2015 年更为严重的危机，凸显出保留现金的必要性，并将当前形势比作“严冬”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/china-steel-industry-in-crisis-as-baowu-warns-of-severe-winter</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 03:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>行业报告指出美国库存下降，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-14</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受行业报告显示美国原油库存大幅下降且中东紧张局势加剧的影响，油价在周二下跌逾 2% 后上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-14</guid>
